channel.title: Runescape 2006-2008
channel.description:
This is my first project on mopar. So please do not flame.
Anyways, less about me, more about my project. The name says it all. I am making Runescape from 2006-2008. I have found a non-delta i will be using, winterlove v1. No Npc's, No Shops, No Minigames, Incorrect Bonus', Some Skills. I chose this because it is about the only non-delta basic source available. All this means, i get to use a 317 deob client, and more coding for me :D :D
[code] Versions -------- Version 1 --------- 11-27-09 ------------ Started My Project
Decided to just call my project - server "runescape"
Changed Login & Death Coords
Added Npc's for lummy, fally, rimmy, varrock, port sarim, barb village, edge, and draynor.
Changed the background to 2006 background.
Changed all sideicons to 2006 icons.
Changed all staticons to 2006 icons. [/code]
[code] Working On Right Now ---------------------
Shops For Lummy & Varrock
[/code]
[code] Pictures -------- None Uploaded Yet, Sorry. [/code]
[code] Videos ------ None Uploaded Yet, Sorry. [/code]
I will post some pictures tommorow. It is getting late and i don't really feel like taking pictures ATM.
This Project Was Start Friday, November 27, 2009. Please Do Not Post Saying I Have Not Done Much, Since This Is New.
